org.apache.hadoop.hbase.master

Class TestWarmupRegion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hbase.master.TestWarmupRegion

  • public class TestWarmupRegion
extends Object
    Run tests that use the HBase clients; HTable. Sets up the HBase mini cluster once at start and runs through all client tests. Each creates a table named for the method and does its stuff against that.
